Drop – Offline Music & Video Player
Privacy Policy
Last updated: March 24, 2025

We at Drop Team are committed to protecting your privacy.

Information We Collect
1.1 Android ID
Used solely as an anonymous internal identifier for syncing your playlists and settings across your own devices.
Stored in hashed, non-reversible form.
1.2 Access to Media Files & Images

READ_MEDIA_AUDIO / VIDEO / IMAGES: Required to play your music/videos and allow you to choose custom cover art from your gallery (with your explicit permission).
1.3 Network Information

Required for displaying direct ads, checking for updates, and downloading themes.
1.4 Analytics & Crash Reports

We use Google Firebase Analytics and Crashlytics (completely anonymous).
Collected data includes: device model, Android version, app version, crash logs, and general usage duration.
1.5 We do NOT upload or store your playlists, playback history, or any media files.

Information We Do NOT Collect
Name, email address, phone number, precise location
Any personal identifiable information
Your media files or playback history
Advertisements
All ads are served directly by Drop Team. We do not use third-party advertising networks.

Permissions Explained

Storage & media permissions → Access your music, videos, and images
REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKAGES & QUERY_ALL_PACKAGES → Install and detect separate theme APKs
INTERNET → Direct ads and updates
FOREGROUND_SERVICE & POST_NOTIFICATIONS → Background playback
SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW → Floating playback window
Data Sharing
Your data is never shared with any third party except:
Google Firebase (anonymous crash and analytics data only)
When required by law or court order
Data Security
All communications are encrypted using HTTPS/TLS. The Android ID is hashed and cannot be reversed.

Children’s Privacy & Age Restriction
The App has no age restriction and is suitable for users of all ages.

Your Rights
You may uninstall the App at any time, which deletes all local data associated with your anonymous account.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
Material changes will be notified via in-app notice or update screen.

Contact us: Khodehydro@gmail.com



